369 DBM calc_collision_matrix(const DBV& r,const DBM& J_inv)
370 {
371  double t3 = -r.z*J_inv(2,2)+r.y*J_inv(3,2);
372  double t7 = -r.z*J_inv(2,3)+r.y*J_inv(3,3);
373  double t12 = -r.z*J_inv(2,1)+r.y*J_inv(3,1);
374  double t21 = r.z*J_inv(1,2)-r.x*J_inv(3,2);
375  double t25 = r.z*J_inv(1,3)-r.x*J_inv(3,3);
376  double t30 = r.z*J_inv(1,1)-r.x*J_inv(3,1);
377  double t39 = -r.y*J_inv(1,2)+r.x*J_inv(2,2);
378  double t43 = -r.y*J_inv(1,3)+r.x*J_inv(2,3);
379  double t48 = -r.y*J_inv(1,1)+r.x*J_inv(2,1);
380  return DBM(
381  1 + -t3*r.z+t7*r.y, t12*r.z-t7*r.x, -t12*r.y+t3*r.x,
382  -t21*r.z+t25*r.y, 1 + t30*r.z-t25*r.x, -t30*r.y+t21*r.x,
383  -t39*r.z+t43*r.y, t48*r.z-t43*r.x, 1 + -t48*r.y+t39*r.x);
384 }

458 {
459  #ifdef MSG_OUT

487  #endif
488 
489  switch(entry_scan_code){

491  if(XKey.Pressed(VK_CONTROL)){

493  if(++indices_entry[curr_entry] >= num_entries)
494  indices_entry[curr_entry] = 0;
495  } while(!(type_entries[indices_entry[curr_entry]] & FIRST_IN_GROUP));
496  break;
497  }
498  if(XKey.Pressed(VK_SHIFT)){
499  if(++curr_entry >= num_indices)
500  curr_entry = 0;
501  break;
502  }
503  if(++indices_entry[curr_entry] >= num_entries)
504  indices_entry[curr_entry] = 0;
505  break;
506  case VK_PRIOR:
507  if(XKey.Pressed(VK_CONTROL)){
508  do{
509  if(--indices_entry[curr_entry] < 0)
510  indices_entry[curr_entry] = num_entries - 1;
511  } while(!(type_entries[indices_entry[curr_entry]] & FIRST_IN_GROUP));
512  break;
513  }
514  if(XKey.Pressed(VK_SHIFT)){
515  if(--curr_entry < 0)
516  curr_entry = num_indices - 1;
517  break;
518  }
519  if(--indices_entry[curr_entry] < 0)
520  indices_entry[curr_entry] = num_entries - 1;
521  break;
522  case VK_ADD:
523  if(XKey.Pressed(VK_CONTROL)){
524  if(++num_indices >= max_indices)
525  num_indices = max_indices;
526  break;
527  }
528  if(type_entries[indices_entry[curr_entry]] & INT_ENTRY)
529  if(XKey.Pressed(VK_SHIFT))
530  (*(int*)pval_entries[indices_entry[curr_entry]])++;
531  else
532  (*(int*)pval_entries[indices_entry[curr_entry]]) += abs((*(int*)pval_entries[indices_entry[curr_entry]]))/16 + 1;
533  else
534  if(XKey.Pressed(VK_SHIFT))
535  *(double*)pval_entries[indices_entry[curr_entry]] *= 1.0002;
536  else
537  *(double*)pval_entries[indices_entry[curr_entry]] *= 1.05;
538  break;
539  case VK_SUBTRACT:
540  if(XKey.Pressed(VK_CONTROL)){
541  if(--num_indices < 0)
542  num_indices = 0;
543  break;
544  }
545  if(type_entries[indices_entry[curr_entry]] & INT_ENTRY)
546  if(XKey.Pressed(VK_SHIFT))
547  (*(int*)pval_entries[indices_entry[curr_entry]])--;
548  else
549  (*(int*)pval_entries[indices_entry[curr_entry]]) -= abs((*(int*)pval_entries[indices_entry[curr_entry]]))/16 + 1;
550  else
551  if(XKey.Pressed(VK_SHIFT))
552  *(double*)pval_entries[indices_entry[curr_entry]] /= 1.0002;
553  else
554  *(double*)pval_entries[indices_entry[curr_entry]] /= 1.05;
555  break;
556  case 'S':
557  if(XKey.Pressed(VK_CONTROL))
558  global_save_parameter(indices_entry[curr_entry]);
559  else{
560  save_parameters(prm_name);
561  save_parameters("common.prm");
562  }
563  break;
564  }
565  entry_scan_code = 0;
566

568  J_inv = (model -> J*(pow(scale_size,2)/model -> volume)).inverse();
569 }

946 inline int get_three_heights(int x,int y)
947 {
948  unsigned char* p = vMap -> lineT[y & clip_mask_y];
949  if(!p)
950  return 255;
951  p += x & clip_mask_x;
952  unsigned char attr = *(p + H_SIZE);
953  if(!(attr & DOUBLE_LEVEL))
954  return *p;
955  //64 bit problem
956  uintptr_t ll = *LOW_LEVEL(p);
957  return ll | (ll + (GET_THICKNESS(p) << 8)) | ((uintptr_t)(*HIGH_LEVEL(p)) << 16) | 0xff000000;
958 }
959 inline int get_upper_height(int x,int y)
960 {
961  unsigned char* p = vMap -> lineT[y & clip_mask_y];
962  if(!p)
963  return 255;
964  p += (x | 1) & clip_mask_x;
965  return *p;
966 }
967 inline int check_double_level(int x,int y)
968 {
969  unsigned char* p = vMap -> lineT[y & clip_mask_y];
970  if(!p)
971  return 0;
972  return p[(x & clip_mask_x) + H_SIZE] & DOUBLE_LEVEL ? 1 : 0;
973 }
974 int trace_shadow(int x,int y,int z)
975 {
976  int x0 = x;
977  z <<= 8;
978  while((z >> 8) > get_upper_height(x,y)){
979  z -= SHADOWDEEP;
980  x--;
981  }
982  return x0 - x;
983 }
984 int set_3D_adjust(int mode,int xx,int yy,int zz,int D)
985 {
986  unsigned char** LineT = vMap -> lineT;
987  unsigned char *p0,*p;
988  int x,y;
989  unsigned int z_sum = 0,u_sum=0,l_sum=0,cnt = 0,db_cnt=0,lh,uh;
990  xx -= (xx - D) & 1;
991  for(y = -D;y <= D;y++){
992  p0 = LineT[(y + yy) & clip_mask_y];
993  if(!p0)
994  continue;
995  for(x = -D;x < D;x += 2){
996  p = (unsigned char *)((uintptr_t)p0 + ((x + xx) & clip_mask_x));
997  if(!(*(p + H_SIZE) & DOUBLE_LEVEL)){
998  z_sum += *p;
999  z_sum += *(p + 1);
1000  cnt += 2;
1001  }
1002  else{
1003  lh = *p;
1004  uh = *(p + 1);
1005  u_sum += uh << 1;
1006  l_sum += lh << 1;
1007  db_cnt += 2;
1008  }
1009  }
1010  }
1011  if(mode == SET_3D_TO_THE_LOWER_LEVEL)
1012  return db_cnt ? l_sum/db_cnt : (cnt ? z_sum/cnt : 255);
1013  if(mode == SET_3D_TO_THE_UPPER_LEVEL)
1014  return db_cnt ? u_sum/db_cnt : (cnt ? z_sum/cnt : 255);
1015  if(mode == SET_3D_CHOOSE_LEVEL)
1016  if(db_cnt){
1017  uh = u_sum/db_cnt;
1018  return zz > (int)uh - 16 ? uh : l_sum/db_cnt;
1019  }
1020  return cnt ? z_sum/cnt : 255;
1021 }

1023 double get_height(int xx,int yy,double z_dbl,int D,DBV& n,int& z_below)
1024 {
1025  unsigned char** LineT = vMap -> lineT;
1026  int double_level_log = 0;
1027  unsigned char *p0,*p;
1028  int zz = round(z_dbl);
1029  int x,y,z = 0,upper_log = 0,z_sum = 0,cnt = 0,lh,mh,uh;
1030  int N0 = 0,N1 = 0;
1031  int Sx0 = 0,Sy0 = 0;
1032  int Sx1 = 0,Sy1 = 0;
1033  int N=0;
1034  int Sx=0,Sx2=0;
1035  int Sy=0,Sy2=0;
1036  int Sz=0;
1037  int Sxz=0,Syz=0;
1038  int zmax = 0;
1039 
1040  int D2 = D*D;
1041  int D3 = D2*D;
1042  int D4 = D3*D;
1043  N = 2*D2 + D;
1044  Sx = -N;
1045  Sx2 = (D4 + D3 + 2*(D + D2))/3;
1046  Sy2 = (2*D4 + D2)/3 + D3;
1047 
1048  xx -= (xx - D) & 1;
1049  for(y = -D;y <= D;y++){
1050  p0 = LineT[(y + yy) & clip_mask_y];
1051  if(!p0)
1052  continue;
1053  for(x = -D;x < D;x += 2){
1054  p = p0 + ((x + xx) & clip_mask_x);
1055  if(!(*(p + H_SIZE) & DOUBLE_LEVEL)){
1056  z = *p;
1057  if((uh = *(p + 1)) > z)
1058  z = uh;
1059  if(zmax < z)
1060  zmax = z;
1061 
1062  if(zz < z){
1063  z_sum += z;
1064  cnt++;
1065  upper_log++;
1066  }
1067  }
1068  else{
1069  lh = *p;
1070 // mh = lh + GET_THICKNESS_ATTR(*(p + H_SIZE),*(p + 1 + H_SIZE));
1071  uh = *(p + 1);
1072  mh = GET_MIDDLE_HIGHT(lh,uh);
1073  if(zz >= mh && zz <= uh){
1074  double_level_log = 1;
1075  if(zz - mh < uh - zz){
1076  z_sum += mh;
1077  cnt++;
1078  upper_log--;
1079  }
1080  else{
1081  z_sum += uh;
1082  cnt++;
1083  upper_log++;
1084  }
1085  }
1086  else{
1087  if(zz < lh){
1088  z_sum += lh;
1089  cnt++;
1090  upper_log++;
1091  }
1092  }
1093 
1094  z = zz >= mh ? uh : lh;
1095  if(zmax < z)
1096  zmax = z;
1097  }
1098 
1099  if(z - zz > MIN_WALL_DELTA){
1100  Sx1 += x; Sy1 += y; N1++;
1101  }
1102  else{
1103  Sx0 += x; Sy0 += y; N0++;
1104  }
1105 
1106  Sz += z;
1107  Sxz += x*z;
1108  Syz += y*z;
1109  }
1110  }
1111 
1112  z_below = zmax;
1113 
1114  if(!cnt)
1115  return -1;
1116 
1117  if(upper_log < 0){
1118  n = DBV(0,0,-1);
1119  return (z_dbl - (double)z_sum/cnt);
1120  }
1121 
1122 // if(N1 > 0 && N0 > 0){
1123 // n = DBV((double)Sx0/(double)N0 - (double)Sx1/(double)N1,(double)Sy0/(double)N0 - (double)Sy1/(double)N1,0);
1124 // n.norm(1);
1125 // return k_elastic_xy*(double)N1;
1126 // }
1127 
1128  if(double_level_log){
1129  n = DBV(0,0,1);
1130  return ((double)zmax - z_dbl);
1131  }
1132 
1133  double Det_x = (double)N*Sx2 - (double)Sx*Sx;
1134  if(fabs(Det_x) < DBL_EPS)
1135  return -1;
1136  double Det_y = (double)N*Sy2 - (double)Sy*Sy;
1137  if(fabs(Det_y) < DBL_EPS)
1138  return -1;
1139  double A = ((double)N*Sxz - (double)Sx*Sz)/Det_x;
1140  double B = ((double)N*Syz - (double)Sy*Sz)/Det_y;
1141  n = DBV(-A,-B,1);
1142  n.norm(1);
1143  return (double)zmax - z_dbl;
1144  //return ((double)zmax - z_dbl)*n.z;
1145 }

1147 int VariablePolygon::lower_average(int xx,int yy,int zz,double& X0,double& Y0,double& dZ0,double& X1,double& Y1,double& dZ1)
1148 {
1149  unsigned char** LineT = vMap -> lineT;
1150  int xl,xr,al,ar,bl,br,d,where,Y;
1151  int x1,x2;
1152  Vertex *lfv,*rfv,*ltv,*rtv;
1153  Vertex **lto,**rto;
1154  Vertex **curr,**beg,**up,**end;
1155  unsigned char *p0,*p;
1156 
1157  beg = up = curr = vertices;
1158  end = vertices + num_vert - 1;
1159  curr++;
1160  for(;curr <= end;curr++)
1161  if((*up) -> yscr_8 > (*curr) -> yscr_8)
1162  up = curr;
1163 
1164  rfv = lfv = *up;
1165  lto = PREV_VERTEX(up);
1166  ltv = *lto;
1167  rto = NEXT_VERTEX(up);
1168  rtv = *rto;
1169 
1170  Y = lfv -> yscr_8; xl = lfv -> xscr_8;
1171  al = ltv -> xscr_8 - xl; bl = ltv -> yscr_8 - Y;
1172  ar = rtv -> xscr_8 - xl; br = rtv -> yscr_8 - Y;
1173  xr = xl = (xl << 16) + (1 << 15);
1174 
1175  DIV16T(al,bl);
1176  DIV16T(ar,br);
1177 
1178  int z,lh,mh,uh,dz,dm,du;
1179  int N = 0;
1180  int N0 = 0,N1 = 0;
1181  int Sx0 = 0,Sy0 = 0;
1182  int Sx1 = 0,Sy1 = 0;
1183  int Sz0 = 0,Sz1 = 0;
1184  while(1){
1185  if(bl > br){
1186  d = br;
1187  where = 0;
1188  }
1189  else{
1190  d = bl;
1191  where = 1;
1192  }
1193  while(d-- > 0){
1194  p0 = LineT[(Y + yy) & clip_mask_y];
1195  if(!p0){
1196  non_loaded_space = 1;
1197  goto cont;
1198  }
1199 
1200  x1 = xl >> 16;
1201  x2 = xr >> 16;
1202 
1203  if(x1 > x2)
1204  SWAP(x1,x2);
1205  x1 &= ~1;
1206  x2 |= 1;
1207  N += (x2 - x1) >> 1;
1208  for(;x1 < x2;x1 += 2){
1209  p = p0 + ((x1 + xx) & clip_mask_x);
1210  if(!(*(p + H_SIZE) & DOUBLE_LEVEL)){
1211  z = *p;
1212  if((uh = *(p + 1)) > z)
1213  z = uh;
1214  if((dz = z - zz) > 0){
1215  if(dz < MIN_WALL_DELTA){
1216  Sx0 += x1; Sy0 += Y; N0++;
1217  Sz0 += dz;
1218  }
1219  else{
1220  Sx1 += x1; Sy1 += Y; N1++;
1221  Sz1 += dz;
1222  }
1223  }
1224  }
1225  else{
1226  lh = *p;
1227  uh = *(p + 1);
1228  if((du = uh - zz) > 0){
1229  mh = GET_MIDDLE_HIGHT(lh,uh);
1230  if((dm = zz - mh) > 0){
1231  if(dm > du){
1232  if(du > MIN_WALL_DELTA){
1233  Sx1 += x1; Sy1 += Y; N1++;
1234  Sz1 += du;
1235  }
1236  else{
1237  Sx0 += x1; Sy0 += Y; N0++;
1238  Sz0 += du;
1239  }
1240  }
1241  }
1242  else{
1243  if((dz = lh - zz) > 0){
1244  if(dz > MIN_WALL_DELTA){
1245  Sx1 += x1; Sy1 += Y; N1++;
1246  Sz1 += dz;
1247  }
1248  else{
1249  Sx0 += x1; Sy0 += Y; N0++;
1250  Sz0 += dz;
1251  }
1252  }
1253  }
1254  }
1255  }
1256  }
1257 
1258  cont:
1259  Y++;
1260  xl += al;
1261  xr += ar;
1262  }
1263 
1264  if(where){
1265  if(ltv == rtv)
1266  goto ret;
1267  lfv = ltv;
1268  lto = PREV_VERTEX(lto);
1269  ltv = *lto;
1270 
1271  br -= bl;
1272 
1273  xl = lfv -> xscr_8;
1274  al = ltv -> xscr_8 - xl;
1275  bl = ltv -> yscr_8 - Y;
1276  xl = (xl << 16) + (1 << 15);
1277 
1278  DIV16T(al,bl);
1279  }
1280  else{
1281  if(rtv == ltv)
1282  goto ret;
1283  rfv = rtv;
1284  rto = NEXT_VERTEX(rto);

1782 int square_analysis(int xx,int yy,double z_dbl,int D,double& dZ,DBV& r,DBV& n)
1783 {
1784  unsigned char** LineT = vMap -> lineT;
1785  unsigned char *p0,*p;
1786  int zz = round(z_dbl);
1787  int x,y,z,dz,upper_log = 0,lh,mh,uh;
1788  int x_sum = 0,y_sum = 0,z_sum = 0,dz_sum = 0,cnt = 0;
1789  int N=0;
1790  int Sx=0,Sx2=0;
1791  int Sy=0,Sy2=0;
1792  int Sz=0;
1793  int Sxz=0,Syz=0;
1794 
1795  int D2 = D*D;
1796  int D3 = D2*D;
1797  int D4 = D3*D;
1798  N = 2*D2 + D;
1799  Sx = -N;
1800  Sx2 = (D4 + D3 + 2*(D + D2))/3;
1801  Sy2 = (2*D4 + D2)/3 + D3;
1802 
1803  xx -= (xx - D) & 1;
1804  for(y = -D;y <= D;y++){
1805  p0 = LineT[(y + yy) & clip_mask_y];

1810  if(!(*(p + H_SIZE) & DOUBLE_LEVEL)){
1811  z = *p;
1812  if((uh = *(p + 1)) > z)
1813  z = uh;
1814  if((dz = z - zz) > 0){
1815  x_sum += x;
1816  y_sum += y;
1817  z_sum += z;
1818  dz_sum += dz;
1819  cnt++;
1820  upper_log++;
1821  }
1822  }
1823  else{
1824  lh = *p;
1825  uh = *(p + 1);
1826  if(zz <= uh){
1827  mh = GET_MIDDLE_HIGHT(lh,uh);
1828  if(zz >= mh){
1829  if(zz - mh < uh - zz){
1830  z = lh;
1831  x_sum += x;
1832  y_sum += y;
1833  z_sum += mh;
1834  dz_sum += mh - zz;
1835  cnt++;
1836  upper_log--;
1837  }
1838  else{
1839  z = uh;
1840  x_sum += x;
1841  y_sum += y;
1842  z_sum += uh;
1843  dz_sum += uh - zz;
1844  cnt++;
1845  upper_log++;
1846  }
1847  }
1848  else{
1849  z = lh;
1850  if((dz = lh - zz) > 0){
1851  x_sum += x;
1852  y_sum += y;
1853  z_sum += lh;
1854  dz_sum += dz;
1855  cnt++;
1856  upper_log++;
1857  }
1858  }
1859  }
1860  else
1861  z = uh;
1862  }
1863 
1864  Sz += z;
1865  Sxz += x*z;
1866  Syz += y*z;
1867  }
1868  }
1869 
1870  if(!cnt)
1871  return 0;

1874  r.x = cnt_inv*x_sum;
1875  r.y = cnt_inv*y_sum;

1881  n = DBV(0,0,1);

1886  n = DBV(0,0,1);
1887  return 1;
1888  }

1890  double B = ((double)N*Syz - (double)Sy*Sz)/Det_y;

1892  n.norm(1);
1893  //dZ *= n.z;

2034  upper_log++;

2100  DIV16T(ar,br);

2111  g_dz_sum += dz_sum;

2125  r.z = cnt_inv*z_sum;

2129  if(fabs(Det_x) < DBL_EPS){

4131 void Object::precise_impulse(Vector source_point,int x_dest,int y_dest)
4132 {
4133  double k = V_drag_stuff;
4134  double dt = ID & ID_VANGER ? dt0 : dt_debris;
4135  double gdt2 = g*dt*dt;
4136  double v0dt = 0;
4137  double V0x,V0y,N;
4138 
4139  double dx = getDistX(x_dest,source_point.x);
4140  double dy = getDistY(y_dest,source_point.y);
4141  int z_dest;
4142  unsigned char* p = vMap -> lineT[y_dest & clip_mask_y];
4143  if(!p)
4144  z_dest = 127;
4145  else
4146  z_dest = p[(x_dest | 1) & clip_mask_x];
4147  double dz = source_point.z - z_dest;
4148  if(dz < 0){
4149  source_point.z = z_dest + 80;
4150  dz = 80;
4151  }
4152 
4153  {
4154  double t1 = log(k);
4155  double t2 = k*k;
4156  double t4 = v0dt*k;
4157  double t8 = 1/gdt2;
4158  double t10 = 1/(k-1.0);
4159  double t23 = t1*t8;

4181 /*******************************************************************************
4182  BOX TO BOX COLLISION TEST
4183 *******************************************************************************/
4184 DBV box_to_box_intersection(DBV RR,DBV X,DBV Y,DBV Z,double sx,double sy,double sz)
4185 {
4186  int i;
4187  DBV R1(0,0,0),R2 = RR;
4188  double x,y,z;
4189  for(i = 0;i < 12;i++){
4190  x = sx*RR.x;
4191  y = sy*RR.y;
4192  z = sz*RR.z;
4193  if(fabs(x) > fabs(y))
4194  if(fabs(x) > fabs(z)){
4195  sx /= 2;
4196  R1.x += x > 0 ? sx : -sx;
4197  }
4198  else{
4199  sz /= 2;
4200  R1.z += z > 0 ? sz : -sz;
4201  }
4202  else
4203  if(fabs(y) > fabs(z)){
4204  sy /= 2;
4205  R1.y += y > 0 ? sy : -sy;
4206  }
4207  else{
4208  sz /= 2;
4209  R1.z += z > 0 ? sz : -sz;
4210  }
4211 
4212  x = X*RR;
4213  y = Y*RR;
4214  z = Z*RR;
4215  if(fabs(x) > fabs(y))
4216  if(fabs(x) > fabs(z)){
4217  X /= 2;
4218  R2 -= x > 0 ? X : -X;
4219  }
4220  else{
4221  Z /= 2;
4222  R2 -= z > 0 ? Z : -Z;
4223  }
4224  else
4225  if(fabs(y) > fabs(z)){
4226  Y /= 2;
4227  R2 -= y > 0 ? Y : -Y;
4228  }
4229  else{
4230  Z /= 2;
4231  R2 -= z > 0 ? Z : -Z;
4232  }
4233  RR = R2 - R1;
4234  }

4237 /*
4238 int obb_disjoint(double B[3][3], double T[3], double a[3], double b[3]);
4239 
4240 This is a test between two boxes, box A and box B. It is assumed that
4241 the coordinate system is aligned and centered on box A. The 3x3
4242 matrix B specifies box B's orientation with respect to box A.
4243 Specifically, the columns of B are the basis vectors (axis vectors) of
4244 box B. The center of box B is located at the vector T. The
4245 dimensions of box B are given in the array b. The orientation and
4246 placement of box A, in this coordinate system, are the identity matrix
4247 and zero vector, respectively, so they need not be specified. The
4248 dimensions of box A are given in array a.
4249 
4250 This test operates in two modes, depending on how the library is
4251 compiled. It indicates whether the two boxes are overlapping, by
4252 returning a boolean.
4253 
4254 The second version of the routine will return a conservative bounds on
4255 the distance between the polygon sets which the boxes enclose. It is
4256 used when RAPID is being used to estimate the distance between two
4257 models.

4802 DBV interpolation(double t,double x[3],DBV y[3])
4803 {
4804  if(fabs(x[1] - x[2]) < DBL_EPS){
4805  if(fabs(x[0] - x[1]) < DBL_EPS)
4806  return y[0];
4807  return (y[0] - y[1])*((t - x[1])/(x[0] - x[1]));
4808  }
4809  if(fabs(x[0] - x[1]) < DBL_EPS)
4810  return (y[1] - y[2])*((t - x[2])/(x[1] - x[2]));
4811 
4812  DBV t3 = x[1]*y[2];
4813  double t8 = x[1]*x[1];
4814  double t11 = x[2]*x[2];
4815  double t12 = x[1]*t11;
4816  double t13 = x[0]*x[0];
4817  DBV t20 = t13*y[1];
4818  DBV t22 = t11*y[1];
4819  DBV t23 = y[2]*t8;
4820  DBV t24 = y[0]*t8;
4821  double t28 = 1/(-x[2]+x[0]);
4822  double t34 = 1/(x[0]*x[1]-x[0]*x[2]-t8+x[2]*x[1]);
4823  DBV A = (y[1]*x[2]-y[1]*x[0]-t3+x[1]*y[0]-y[0]*x[2]+x[0]*y[2])/(t8*x[2]-t8*x[0]-t12+x[1]*t13-t13*x[2]+x[0]*t11);
4824  DBV B = -(-t20+t13*y[2]+t22-t23+t24-y[0]*t11)*t28*t34;
4825  DBV C = (t3*t13-t20*x[2]-t23*x[0]+t22*x[0]+t24*x[2]-t12*y[0])*t28*t34;
4826  return (A*t + B)*t + C;
4827 }

4829 DBV interpolation_factors(double t,double x[3])
4830 {
4831  if(fabs(x[1] - x[2]) < DBL_EPS){
4832  if(fabs(x[0] - x[1]) < DBL_EPS)
4833  return DBV(1,0,0);
4834  double t1 = t - x[1]/(x[0] - x[1]);
4835  return DBV(t1, 1-t1, 0);
4836  }
4837  if(fabs(x[0] - x[1]) < DBL_EPS){
4838  double t1 = t - x[2]/(x[1] - x[2]);
4839  return DBV(0,t1, 1-t1);
4840  }
4841 
4842  double t1 = x[0]*x[0];
4843  double t2 = x[1]*t1;
4844  double t3 = x[1]*x[1];
4845  double t4 = t3*x[0];
4846  double t7 = 1/(-x[2]+x[0]);
4847  double t13 = 1/(x[0]*x[1]-x[0]*x[2]-t3+x[2]*x[1]);
4848  double t19 = t3*x[2];
4849  double t20 = x[2]*x[2];
4850  double t21 = x[1]*t20;
4851  double t22 = t1*x[2];
4852  double t23 = x[0]*t20;
4853  double t25 = 1/(t19-t4-t21+t2-t22+t23);
4854  return DBV((-t21+t19)*t7*t13+(-(t3-t20)*t7*t13+(x[1]-x[2])*t25*t)*t,
4855  (-t22+t23)*t7*t13+(-(t20-t1)*t7*t13+(x[2]-x[0])*t25*t)*t,
4856  (t2-t4)*t7*t13+(-(-t3+t1)*t7*t13+(-x[1]+x[0])*t25*t)*t);
4857 }
